      "instruction": "<p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous amount of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Cover with a lid and cook for 5-8 min or until the linguine is cooked</p><p>Tip: Keep checking that the linguine has not stuck to the base of the pot and stir if needed</p>",
